 get started with the Android Support Library v26, which includes a variety=
 of new features including fonts as resources, downloadable fonts, emoji su=
pport, an autosizing TextView, physics driven animations via Spring and Fli=
ng, and backwards compatibility for animated vectors.  <http://mkto-o0039.c=
om/f00o50d0Ov015O4AJQXY30S>


