r Executive at Microsoft, will provide an overview of emerging technologies=
 such as cognitive services, bot frameworks, machine learning, and digital =
reality, and will showcase examples of how these capabilities are raising t=
he bar for mobile apps and elevating customer expectations. November 9, Bos=
ton, MA, USA <http://mkto-o0039.com/Q0oX0OO0Jw4dA1Q5500ZS30>

